  "title": "chore(storybook): migrate dev-novel to storybook",
  "body": "This migrates our stories from `dev-novel` to `storybook`.\r\n\r\nThe global environment variable `__DEV__` respects the storybook environment (set to `false` when deployed and `true` when developing).\r\n\r\nLink to storybook: https://deploy-preview-3376--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/stories\r\n\r\nCloses #3051\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n⚠️ This will need to be deployed (therefore merged) at the same time as the corresponding documentation deployment after having updated the story links in the doc.",
